                              'Xcenter' 1.02

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'XCenter' is a @{" game " link play} where you find yourself on an island located
in the center of a lake and you want to go to the shore, that is, on
the border of the lake. To succeed, there must be an uninterrupted
series of islands lined-up horizontally or vertically from the center 
of one of the border tiles.

  Have fun!

