@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place "XCenter" where you want on
your hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc. No other files or Libraries
are needed.

                             How to play?

  To play, click on the rectangular shaped islands that randomly appear
on the lake, this cause some other islands to appear or disappear.

  When an uninterrupted series of islands is formed between the central
island and one of the border tiles, a 'path' is created on the islands
and the game ends. Afterward XCenter displays the number of moves you
have made in the game. Try to complete the game in the least amount of
moves possible.

  A percentage indicator is displayed under the game board, that
percentage represents the ratio of islands in relation to the total
game area.

  Have fun!

OPTIONS

  On the lower portion of the game window, the following buttons are shown:

-New Game            -Restarts the game.

-About               -Displays the informations about 'XCenter'.

